c: 17
v: 62
t: "Ibliis Yallal koroositak yi Rabbow yoh warisey A seehadaytuy yol muxxussey konnabah kummaata kah itte yol kah muxxussem? Atu Qhiyaamah ayrô fanah yoo wadirrossek, diggah kay samad ku gitak makkoyseyyooh amol keenik gaceyyooh ken bayseyyo, dago maray isi qibaadah keenik caglissey umaanek dacrisse akke waytek iyye"